title: ‘Elect Hillary President, You Have A Country That Goes To Hell’
text: Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump is adamant that Democrat presidential candidate Hillary Clinton should not be America’s next president. In fact, the real estate mogul said during a Saturday afternoon speech in Jacksonville, Florida, that the country would “go to hell” should Clinton win the 2016 election.
